          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_LookupAgencyAndFacilityInformation_Updated",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve information about facilities and their associated agencies based on a user's email address and optional search criteria. It supports pagination and sorting of results, and logs the usage of the report for auditing purposes. The procedure fetches data from several tables, including "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Account",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Facility",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Meter",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and filters results based on active accounts and optional search text."
        }
      ]
